lead_paragraph: Sophie Brunner had 14 points with 10 rebounds and Arizona State made its last nine shots and scored the last six points of the game to defeat No. 19 Florida 69-63 on Sunday to win the ASU Classic.

headline.print_headline: Arizona St Women Make Last 9 Shots, Rally by No. 19 Florida
